         * drawable.

variables.name: SOLID_COLORED
variables.comment: * A style identifier indicating that the updatable drawable has a solid color fill.

variables.name: SOLID_NOT_COLORED
variables.comment:
* A style identifier indicating that the updatable drawable has a solid non-colored
             * fill.
